"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"FAUNA:4.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">4.2</span> 標題：爬行動物（reptiles [crawling and creeping things]）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來：זחל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯：zachal)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:24\">DEU 32:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:17\">MIC 7:17</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來：רֶמֶשׂ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯：remes)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:24\">GEN 1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:25\">GEN 1:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26\">GEN 1:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:7\">GEN 6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:20\">GEN 6:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:14\">GEN 7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:23\">GEN 7:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:19\">GEN 8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:3\">GEN 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:13\">1KI 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:25\">PSA 104:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:10\">PSA 148:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:10\">EZK 8:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:20\">EZK 38:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:20\">HOS 2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:14\">HAB 1:14</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來：שֶׁרֶץ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯：sherets)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:21\">GEN 7:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev5:2\">LEV 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:10\">LEV 11:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:20\">LEV 11:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:21\">LEV 11:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:23\">LEV 11:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:29\">LEV 11:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:31\">LEV 11:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:41\">LEV 11:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:42\">LEV 11:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:43\">LEV 11:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:44\">LEV 11:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:5\">LEV 22:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἑρπετόν</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯：herpeton)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:12\">ACT 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:6\">ACT 11:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:23\">ROM 1:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:7\">JAS 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir10:11\">SIR 10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EpJer1:20\">LJE 1:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Latin</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">拉：reptilis</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd6:53\">2ES 6:53</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">討論</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>希伯來文<em>zachal</em> 和<em>remes</em> 字面義為「爬行的（東西）」，用來指稱體型較小的不潔淨生物，特別是爬行動物。希伯來文<em>sherets</em> 字面義為「成群的東西」，指成群結隊、貼近地面移動的哺乳動物和爬行動物。在以色列，有些蝰蛇產下的幼蛇生活在離彼此不遠的地方，直到完全成熟。到了交配季節，這些蛇又再次聚集在一起。這些蝰蛇都包含在<em>sherets</em> 一詞中。希臘文<em>herpeton</em> 也是對爬行動物的通稱，包括蛇和蜥蜴。通常，所有的希伯來文、希臘文和拉丁文意指「爬行動物」的詞語，都排除了魚的意思，除了<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:20\">GEN 1:20</a> 這個可能的例外。</p>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">特殊意義或象徵意義</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>這些希伯來文詞語含有禮儀上不潔淨的意思。</p>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>如果目標語言有意為「爬行動物」的詞語，那麼該詞可以用在大多數經文中。在沒有這個詞的語言中，可以使用「蛇和蜥蜴」、「蠕動的東西」等短語。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
